http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Recruitment/article13998641.ece

Superintendent of Police S. Chandrashekar Reddy said that for the first time after the formation of Telangana, the government was conducting recruitment for Stipendiary Cadet Trainee Constable posts on a large scale.Calling upon youth to make use of the opportunity, he asked them to apply online on www.tslprb.in and get all the details before submitting the application. He also appealed to them not to believe in middlemen trying to hoodwink genuine applicants.If the applicants have any doubts, they can approach a nearby police station to get clarification, he added.